## Rules

1. **Do not edit** `src/games/<id>/` or `games/<id>/` for any stable game unless the user **explicitly** asks.
2. **Prefer shared code** for cross-game fixes: `freeQuizShell.ts`, `freeGameShell.ts`, `freeShellNav.ts`, `_quiz/style.css`, `_casual/style.css`, `game-shell.css`, `tournamentGameFlow.ts`, i18n.
3. **Notify the user** when a shared-platform change will affect a stable game (which file changed and which games pick it up).
4. Copy patterns from stable games into new titles — do not refactor stable game code to share logic.

Per-game rules also live in `.cursor/rules/*-stable.mdc`.
